00:28:13.740 --> 00:28:15.240
I like the way you're
holding the future open

00:28:15.240 --> 00:28:16.311
for good things.

00:28:16.311 --> 00:28:17.275
(class laughs)

00:28:17.275 --> 00:28:19.500
That's awesome. That's really good.

